title: Fuente Fuente Rarities
itunes:title: Fuente Fuente Rarities
description: This week we're smoking Arturo Fuente rarities; rare cigars that only come out once a year, in very small amounts. We start off with the Arturo Fuente "Between the Line." Hemmingway or NOT Hemmingway? That is the question. In the second hour we light up the Arturo Feunte Anejo #55. Two phenomenal cigars, but why not make them all the time? We'll tell you why, and look ahead to what's on the horizon for 2013.
